title: Three cheese spinach filo rolls
ingredients: ['300g (11 oz) frozen spinach, thawed and squeezed dry', '350g (12 oz) cottage cheese', '5 tablespoons freshly grated Parmesan cheese', '225g (8 oz) grated Gouda cheese', '1 egg, lightly beaten', '1 onion, chopped', '2 sheets filo pastry, thawed']
